<HEAD>Mother Saves Baby By Shoving Carriage Out of Way</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A mother's desperate push saved the life of a
2-month-old boy in a stroller, but the mother was killed when she
couldn't dodge a car steered by an allegedly drunken driver.
   The car, going in reverse at high speed, struck and killed
