<DOCNO> AP890724-0148 </DOCNO>
<FILEID>AP-NR-07-24-89 2030EDT</FILEID>
<FIRST>r w BC-Bush-OutdoorList     07-24 0634</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Bush-Outdoor List,740</SECOND>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here is a list of winners of ``Take Pride in
America'' awards presented by President Bush on Monday.
   Alabama: The First National Bank of Jasper; Boy Scout Troop 29,
Alabama School for the Deaf; The Keep Choctaw County Beautiful
Committee; The Lawrence County Anti-Litter Campaign.
   Arizona: The Arizona Public Service Company; Mountaineers,
